c5","fullItemName":"How this topic was developed","slug":"how-this-topic-was-developed","subChapters":[{"id":"0aa676f7-343f-5fcc-b5ae-cbdff070eb86","slug":"search-strategy","fullItemName":"Search strategy"},{"id":"c4da17f2-12fb-59ac-be32-b10d7da360b5","slug":"stakeholder-engagement","fullItemName":"Stakeholder engagement"},{"id":"0f82fd8b-82f4-5d12-8c6f-044d21628edc","slug":"evidence-exclusion-criteria","fullItemName":"Evidence exclusion criteria"},{"id":"881feb2e-6862-57b2-9c84-650136d4604e","slug":"organizational-behavioural-financial-barriers","fullItemName":"Organizational, behavioural and financial barriers"},{"id":"23a8e26b-fd6f-5bce-bd0f-169e08be2c98","slug":"declarations-of-interest","fullItemName":"Declarations of interest"}]},{"id":"d6105ea0-66a6-5bd6-9d2c-edc57bdc708d","fullItemName":"References","slug":"references","subChapters":[]}]},"parentChapter":{"id":"0e772b83-eb60-572c-8aba-eda986114860","slug":"diagnosis","fullItemName":"Diagnosis"},"subChapters":[{"id":"e7c601d3-b5cf-5ad4-9d2f-e93f1dd2dca1","slug":"basis-for-recommendation-516","fullItemName":"Basis for recommendation","depth":3,"htmlHeader":"<!-- begin field 28627bc9-fbb6-4732-86b2-e4ceb1066175 --><h3>Basis for recommendation</h3><!-- end field 28627bc9-fbb6-4732-86b2-e4ceb1066175 -->","summary":null,"htmlStringContent":"<!-- begin item 51644244-ccf9-40fb-b7bf-91ad8f50bf44 --><!-- begin field 80e8d824-1e1e-4831-b1d3-6c34ccc446bf --><p>The recommendations on the diagnosis of the common cold in adults and older children are based on the National Institute for Health and Care Excellence (NICE) guideline <em>Respiratory tract infections (self-limiting): prescribing antibiotics</em> [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/common-cold/references/\">NICE, 2008</a>]; literature review and expert opinion in the Institute for Clinical Systems Improvement guideline <em>Diagnosis and Treatment of Respiratory Illness in Children and Adults</em> [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/common-cold/references/\">ICSI, 2013</a>]; and expert opinion in the British Medical Journal (BMJ) Best practice review <em>Common cold</em> [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/common-cold/references/\">BMJ, 2016</a>] and in review articles on the common cold [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/common-cold/references/\">Heikkinen and Jarvinen, 2003</a>; <a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/common-cold/references/\">Tolan and Nguyen, 2007</a>; <a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/common-cold/references/\">Worrall, 2011</a>; <a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/common-cold/references/\">Passioti et al, 2014</a>; <a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/common-cold/references/\">Allan, 2014</a>].</p><!-- end field 80e8d824-1e1e-4831-b1d3-6c34ccc446bf --><!-- end item 51644244-ccf9-40fb-b7bf-91ad8f50bf44 -->","subChapters":[]}]}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3666801979"]}